snippet.title: Space Mercs - Beta Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Space Mercs goes in Beta for Linux on May 20th 2019! Join us on discord for a chance to join the beta! Or back us up on patreon to make sure!

Discord: https://discord.gg/VVhVdRt
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/BeardedGiantGames
Bearded Giant Games: http://beardedgiant.games/
Announcement post: https://beardedgiant.games/space-mercs-linux-beta-on-the-20th-of-may/
